Source.Name: lldb
Source.Summary: High performance debugger, part of the LLVM project.
Source.Description: LLDB is a next generation, high-performance debugger. It is built as a set of reusable components which highly leverage existing libraries in the larger LLVM Project, such as the Clang expression parser and LLVM disassembler.
